                    <div class="activity-card">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-users"></i> Hackathons</h3>
                        <p>Joined hackathons to collaborate with peers, generate ideas quickly, and turn prototypes into working products under pressure.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="activity-card">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i> Workshops</h3>
                        <p>Organized and led workshops that helped beginners learn web development concepts and develop confidence with code.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>MyPortfolio</h3>
                    <p>Showcasing my journey in technology and development.</p>
                </div>
